          <li><strong>Mellow Mode</strong> - 10am - 10am, A relaxed challenge for the players, with the option to drop in and out at certain campaign points.</li>
          <li><strong>Mix Mode</strong> - Mainly for videogame streamers, as many hours as you can physically do from 1 to 48 hours depending on the amount of challenge you can manage.</li>
        </ul>
